  <brief_title>Observation Study of the Medication Switch at Patients Treated With Sitaxentan to a Regime Without Sitaxentan</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Devolution of a Medication Change at Patients With Mono- or Combination Therapy With Sitaxentan to a Regime Without Sitaxentan.</official_title>
